To implement a secure login mechanism with multi-factor authentication (MFA), we will build upon the existing authentication and security structure. We will introduce services to handle MFA, including generating and verifying time-based one-time passwords (TOTP).

Epic Title: User Authentication and Security

We will create necessary files within the `backend/authentication` directories: `services` for MFA, `controllers` for login flow, and extend the existing models for handling MFA data.

